{"tid":1722743,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又一藍絲","createTime":"2019-11-15T03:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T03:47:30.000Z","uid":25327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dcadc47134277d2822aeca19ddd96e61c42f7f80","tid":1722743,"uid":25327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GYWYHXZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGYWYHXZ.png&h=4959c778&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩係樓下食飯，條撚樣講話黑衣人阻住佢搵食，開三鎗邊度夠，最好就拎機關鎗掃曬d暴徒<br />\n<br />\n其實平時行街呢d都聽得多，我都廢時理<br />\n<br />\n不過佢一講話d女暴徒係天使，要捉曬去強姦果下我就真係忍唔住要起身過去同佢澄清一下根本冇d咁既事，唔好係度亂講<br />\n<br />\n佢又作勢想打鳩我又叫罵又剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個事頭婆就叫我走先<br />\n<br />\n咁我就敗走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因為我見佢都幾大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過天有眼，岩岩無聊開line果陣people nearby竟然搵佢佢個撚頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就希望大家見到此人就唔好鶳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我驚比佢打死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468bba979adfbeb2b9b6e21fef0d7b86c5ca1364","tid":1722743,"uid":249015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}